name: As Above...
description:
A primitive demon, obviously with some bipolar problems. This is its smiling side.

-------------

It is a woodcut, carved on wood panel found near garbage cans in Helsinki (like balloon head, but it was not the same type of wood). Its wood quality was really bad, which turned to be an advantage to add all those textures and splinters effects.

It was also printed without having access to a printing press : I did it the old way, with a wooden spoon on the floor. 

-------------

60x60 cm, woodcut print

2800x2890px
